{"id":6487,"date":"2024-01-11T10:57:19","date_gmt":"2020-03-11T05:27:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=6487"},"modified":"2022-06-21T12:45:23","modified_gmt":"2022-06-21T07:15:23","slug":"blue-bedroom-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/blue-bedroom-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Design Ideas For Breezy Vibes: Refreshing Blue Bedrooms To Unwind In"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Shed those blues with these rejuvenating blue bedroom ideas!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Agree or not, you definitely have that tiny soft corner for the blue colour, right? It is serene, soothing and calms you down in minutes after a tough day at work. That\u2019s why, for your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interiors<\/a>, especially for your bedroom, blue is the perfect colour.&nbsp; Not too boring or bland, blue perks up your walls and uplifts the vibe of your chamber like no other colour. Need inspiration and quick ideas to paint it all blue? These blue bedroom color ideas will win you over in no time! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Cooler Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A softer shade or a mix of blue and white paint will truly liven up those walls of yours. This palette is both easy on the eyes and evokes a soothing vibe. Like old wine, this shade of blue grows on you and before you know it, you fall in love with all its coolness and then some more. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011757\/cooler-blue-bedroom-walls.jpg\" alt=\"Cooler blue bedroom that a softer shade or a mix of blue and white paint will genuinely liven up those walls of yours.\" class=\"wp-image-6493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011757\/cooler-blue-bedroom-walls.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011757\/cooler-blue-bedroom-walls-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011757\/cooler-blue-bedroom-walls-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011757\/cooler-blue-bedroom-walls-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Go for a cooler shade of blue and interplay it with white for a calming atmosphere<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Bohemian Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Perfect for a maverick teenager or an imaginative young adult\u2019s cozy bedroom, this shade of blue instantly sparks ideas in your mind. Pair it up with wall art or graffiti and your eyes are up for a treat without a doubt. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011741\/blue-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Bohemian blue bedroom ideas make pair it up with a shade of blue and wall art or graffiti, and your eyes are up for a treat without a doubt.\" class=\"wp-image-6489\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011741\/blue-bedroom-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011741\/blue-bedroom-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011741\/blue-bedroom-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011741\/blue-bedroom-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Choose a slightly unique shade of blue to create a stunning bedroom for young adults and teens.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pantone\u2019s Colour Of The Year &#8211; Classic Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for that shade of blue that is tasteful? We vouch for this one and so does <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/pantone-colour-of-the-year-2020\/\">Pantone<\/a>! Fabulously balanced and soothing, a sweep of this shade of blue on your bedroom wall can never really go wrong. Call dibs on this one if you like to keep it simple, natural and slightly peppy at the same time. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011753\/classic-blue-paint-colors-for-bedrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Classic blue paint colors for bedroom fabulously balanced and soothing, a sweep of this shade of blue on your wall can never really go wrong. \" class=\"wp-image-6492\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011753\/classic-blue-paint-colors-for-bedrooms.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011753\/classic-blue-paint-colors-for-bedrooms-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011753\/classic-blue-paint-colors-for-bedrooms-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011753\/classic-blue-paint-colors-for-bedrooms-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Straight out of Pantone\u2019s shade card this colour is classic and relevant for your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Vintage Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For understated charm in your chamber, a lighter and slightly off shade of blue makes absolute sense. This shade of blue grant&#8217;s old-world feels to your bedroom yet makes it look classy as well. Moreover, it also goes well with the overall white decor of your bedroom. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011819\/vintage-blue-bedroom-decorating-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Vintage blue bedroom walls colour make grants old-world feel to your bedroom yet make it look classy as well.\" class=\"wp-image-6499\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011819\/vintage-blue-bedroom-decorating-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011819\/vintage-blue-bedroom-decorating-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011819\/vintage-blue-bedroom-decorating-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011819\/vintage-blue-bedroom-decorating-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Not too old, not so edgy, this vintage shade of blue is perfect for a balanced and pacifying bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Dreamy Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Perfect for that deep slumberful night for your little one, this shade of blue is what dreams are made up of! It will help your kid unwind and fall into a good night\u2019s sleep. And this is the first part of the story as it also triggers joy at every sight. Just what you need to for a peaceful kids\u2019 bedroom, no? <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011800\/dreamy-blue-bedroom-color-schemes.jpg\" alt=\"Dreamy blue paint for bedroom, this shade of blue is what dreams are made up of! It will help your kid unwind and fall into a good night\u2019s sleep.\" class=\"wp-image-6494\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011800\/dreamy-blue-bedroom-color-schemes.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011800\/dreamy-blue-bedroom-color-schemes-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011800\/dreamy-blue-bedroom-color-schemes-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011800\/dreamy-blue-bedroom-color-schemes-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Almost as cool as snowfall, this shade of blue triggers joy in your kids\u2019 room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Soothing Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>All lovers of earthy shades out there, you are absolutely going to love this shade of blue for your bedroom. With the right mix of texture and hue, this shade makes your bedroom look outstanding without a doubt. Mix it up with a white bed and matching decor and you will rest like a true blue royal every night. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011811\/soothing-blue-and-white-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Blue and white bedroom colour where with the right mix of texture and hue, this shade makes your bedroom look outstanding without a doubt.\" class=\"wp-image-6497\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011811\/soothing-blue-and-white-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011811\/soothing-blue-and-white-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011811\/soothing-blue-and-white-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011811\/soothing-blue-and-white-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Interplay those blue walls with soothing whites and matching furnishings for that soothing slice of the blue bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Aqua, The Refreshing Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>That first sight of aqua just sorts everything out for you at the end of the day, right? So, on the same lines, choose a finely rejuvenating shade of aqua for your bedroom. It is undoubtedly one of the best shades of blue. Pair it with the green, white and fill in some patterns and you have got yourself a perfect haven of serenity. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011736\/blue-bedroom-colors-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Aqua blue bedroom designs are one of the best colour and pair it with the green and white a perfect haven of serenity.\" class=\"wp-image-6488\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011736\/blue-bedroom-colors-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011736\/blue-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011736\/blue-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011736\/blue-bedroom-colors-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Suit up your bedroom with the touch of aqua blue, patterns, and white furniture and rejoice at its sight!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Peppy Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Beat mood swings and bad days with this joyous shade of blue any day. If peppy is on your mind, then choose this shade any day. Deck up those walls with suitable mirror work, the right furnishings and you will need nothing more to unwind in your chamber. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011804\/peppy-blue-paint-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Peppy blue bedroom decorating ideas try to deck up those walls with suitable mirror work, and you will need nothing more to unwind in your chamber.\" class=\"wp-image-6495\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011804\/peppy-blue-paint-for-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011804\/peppy-blue-paint-for-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011804\/peppy-blue-paint-for-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011804\/peppy-blue-paint-for-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Mirrors, a pepped up shade of blue on your walls and just the right furnishings make for a classy bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Subtle Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pastels and minimalism go hand in hand, any given day. Take inspiration from the same and create this bedroom of your dreams in no time. Sky blue walls with suitable wallpaper, pastel decor add up to make this type of bedroom more comforting. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011815\/subtle-light-blue-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Sky blue bedroom walls with suitable wallpaper, pastel decor add up to make this type of bedroom more comforting.\" class=\"wp-image-6498\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011815\/subtle-light-blue-bedroom.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011815\/subtle-light-blue-bedroom-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011815\/subtle-light-blue-bedroom-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011815\/subtle-light-blue-bedroom-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>For a lighter bedroom, choose sky blue for the walls and pair with pastel decor and indie wallpaper to bring in some texture.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want a bedroom that's modern and aesthetic\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09145522\/want-a-bedroom-thats-modern-and-aesthetic.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Bolder Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A darker shade of blue never really goes wrong. For cozy feels and laid back vibes, it is an ideal colour for your chamber. So, if you are still searching for one of the best blue bedroom colours, then trust us, you need to check this shade out as it goes well with all types of wooden furniture and knick-knacks as well. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011749\/bold-blue-bedroom-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Royal blue bedroom, for cosy feels and laid back vibes, it is an ideal colour for your chamber.\" class=\"wp-image-6491\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011749\/bold-blue-bedroom-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011749\/bold-blue-bedroom-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011749\/bold-blue-bedroom-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011749\/bold-blue-bedroom-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption>Bold blue walls and chic furniture create a bedroom that you will never want to leave<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, guess what? With so many blue bedroom colours and options to decorate your bedroom, there is simply no limit to which you can transform a dull den into a heavenly chamber! Take our word then and put our tips to use. And for more help, you can always book our consultation, remember?<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/wall-painting-techniques\/\">Latest Wall Painting Techniques<\/a> <\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/green-room-paint-ideas\/\">Green Room Colours For Your Home<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/master-bedroom-colour-ideas\/\">Master Bedroom Colour Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n            